within target range. Additionally, an electrocardiogram and serum electrolyte levels should also be obtained prior to initiating osilodrostat therapy and periodically thereafter.', 'Metabolism', 'The manufacturer recommends reducing the dosage of osilodrostat by one-half during concomitant use of a potent CYP450 3A4 inhibitor.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/148417/', '', 'Caspofungin, Micafungin, Amphotericin B, Miconazole, Oteseconazole, Flucytosine, Anidulafungin', '', 1767369485);
